node.text:
As part of their campaign to plant 1 million trees a year, Endura agreed to plant an extra 100 trees for every second I can keep my back wheel in the air! Gave it my best shot and my arms are still feeling it! Big up to @enduraofficial for their journey to become carbon neutral by 2024! 
#endura

node.text:
Excited to show you guys my new mtb discipline 😉 “HIGHLAND WARRIOR TM” . It’s a mix of extreme enduro and Speed Trials all mashed together on a sketchy wee course in the garden haha!  Would love to see some courses you guys build your selves, please tag them with the hashtag #highlandwarrior !! Look forward to seeing what you all come up with! 
Filmed by @sempley_rory on my @gopro Hero8
#highlandwarrior #speedtrials #extremeenduro #fun

node.title: HIGHLAND WARRIOR  EXTREME ENDURO SPEED TRIALS OBSTACLE COURSE

node.text:
As a wise man once said “Put it in low box and give’er death” 

It was actually pretty cool to be able to ride back up @lagganwolftrax’s infamous “Ayers Rock” on my heckler 16 years after doing a photo shoot jumping into it on my original @santacruzbicycles Aluminium mtb which laggan still used today to promote the trail centre haha! 

Emtb isn’t about making riding easier, if you put the same energy you put into your mtb they can really do amazing things!! ⚡️⚡️

🎥 @elevationcycles  @frasermcneil 

#lagganwolftrax #mtb @emtb #climbing #heckler #highlands #Scotland

Trailer scrub...

This was the first time I managed to get a full rotation with the @toutterrain trailer while filming for “Daycare”. It took several days of trial and error over a few months to get to this point. 
It’s such a cool feeling when you realise your (mad) idea is actually going to work haha! 

Shout out to @johnbaileyvision @georgeeccleston @rcrompton @davesummertime and @unit23official for making it happen! 

🎥 @davesummertime
